featured_reviews.review_id:
Well maintained. What is best is that you can spot it easily the moment you get out of Kota railway station, even in the night as it is well lit and decorated.
The road to mosque is well paved and clean so you can walk anytime from station to it.
However you need to search for the entry gate as there is market around it, which is not big pain.
